commit.message: Modified code to detect when the phone should be charged.  Added a routine to the initialization that sets the alarm time to one minute ahead of the current time.  Removed setting the RTC current time at the beginning of the program, as the battery backup function is working.
Noah made it actually sound like an alarm clock

Wrote setChargeTime which assumes it takes 70 minutes to charge from 40 to full. Test it and write in leftover commented pseudocode.
